data.whatILove:
HOME LISTED WITH HALL REALTY
PLEASE CALL (410) 957-1888 
Take a look at this well maintained home at the end of a cul-de-sac on a quiet street. The home features 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. Inside, the living room has cathedral ceilings that makes this nice size room feel even larger. The kitchen is centrally located which opens up into the living room and the separate dining room . All 3 rooms have that open feel concept but are separate. The kitchen and dining room have new flooring. The master bed and bath are located in the back which provide a quiet haven from the rest of the house. Some of the features include cathedral ceiling in the bedroom, walk in closet large vanity with 2 sinks and bathtub w/shower. Outside, relax on the covered front porch or spend time entertaining on your large side deck. The side and back yards are fenced in with a privacy fence to keep kids , pets or both safely in. The trees in the back provide relief on those hot summer days. Other features include an above ground pool, shed and a paved driveway. The property is a short distance from shopping, restaurants and downtown. Conveniently located near NASA, Chincotegue , Ocean City and the beaches. Take a look for yourself and see what this great home offers.
